<h5 id="subject_882212">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=36cfbc428e4e74d2e72d6e446257e0fc&amp;topic=94600.msg882212#msg882212" rel="nofollow">Re: 巫师神探加速版   Dresden files accelerated  中文翻译</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_882212'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_882212'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #38 于:</strong> 2017-10-01, 周日 11:16:57 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_882212_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
